# Reporting

**Route:** `reporting` · **Arch phase:** 4 · See `ARCHITECTURE.md` §7

## Purpose

Centralized reporting for earning, redemption, manual operations, pembukuan, and reconciliation.

## Current state

Tab bar with 6 report types. Content area is dashed placeholder. Only tab switching works.

## Report tabs

| Tab | Description | Arch. data source |
|-----|-------------|-------------------|
| Earning Poin | Earning point reports | `fact_point_transaction` (EARN) |
| Redemption Poin | Redemption point reports | `fact_point_transaction` (REDEEM) |
| Manual Adjustment | Manual point adjustments | `manual_adjustment` |
| Manual Redemption | Manual redemption ops | Separate manual ops table |
| Hasil pemrosesan pembukuan | Bookkeeping results | Posting job-run log |
| Hasil rekonsiliasi sistem | Reconciliation results | `reconciliation_run` |

## Planned scope (per tab)

Report table, filters, export actions, reconciliation status.

